Plot
The movie , set in 1967 , is about the real - life sheriff Buford Pusser , who goes after a criminal who has killed young people with his illegal moonshine .
Brian Dennehy plays Pusser .
The rest of the cast include Ken Howard , Sheree North , Forrest Tucker , and Brian Kerwin .
The film was originally entitled " The Letter of the Law " ( which appears in the closing credits ) and was released on VHS as " Hard Stick " .
